					<description><![CDATA[<p>Online Application for Punjab Good Governance Fellowship Programme 2025 About Punjab Good Governance Fellowship Programme 2025: The Government of Punjab</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://applyfornaukri.com/punjab-good-governance-fellowship-programme-2025/">Punjab Good Governance Fellowship Programme 2025</a> first appeared on <a href="https://applyfornaukri.com">Apply For Naukri</a>.</p>]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class="has-text-align-center has-black-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-0ef61c9545a1575be395f068ccb6f3b7" style="background-color:#ed6b6b"><strong>Online Application for Punjab Good Governance Fellowship Programme 2025</strong></p>



<figure class="wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex">
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img data-recalc-dims="1" fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" width="800" height="171" data-id="11167" src="https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/PGGFP.jpg?resize=800%2C171&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-11167" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/PGGFP.jpg?w=885&amp;ssl=1 885w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/PGGFP.jpg?resize=300%2C64&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/PGGFP.jpg?resize=768%2C164&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/PGGFP.jpg?resize=150%2C32&amp;ssl=1 150w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /></figure>
</figure>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-450f099b8393cc8110bdb92d4ee79a65"><strong>About Punjab Good Governance Fellowship Programme 2025</strong>:</p>



<p class="">The Government of Punjab is calling for applications from skilled and enthusiastic individuals for the role of Senior Good Governance Fellows. The Punjab Good Governance Fellowship Programme is a key initiative by the Government of Punjab aimed at creating social impact while offering fellows essential mentorship and exposure. Chosen fellows will acquire practical experience collaborating with senior government officials on significant governance and policy projects across various departments. This also serves as a chance to learn about best practices and the implementation of policies at the district level.</p>



<p class="">Through this two-year fellowship, 50 emerging professionals will be assigned to different administrative departments as Senior Punjab Good Governance Fellows at both the state and district levels. Their role will involve offering strategic and operational assistance in essential priority areas, facilitating governance reforms, and enhancing project implementation, all while acquiring valuable training and experience.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-1d8680557ba3d43a8456b177862a79e9"><strong>Fellowship Name, No. of Vacancy, Qualification:</strong></p>



<figure class="wp-block-table"><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>Fellowship Name</strong></td><td><strong>No. of Vacancy</strong></td><td><strong><strong>Qualification</strong></strong></td></tr><tr><td>Punjab Good Governance Fellowship </td><td>50</td><td>This fellowship is open to individuals who have completed postgraduate studies at a recognized university and have three years of work experience, or to graduates from a reputable university with four years of professional experience. <br><br>Postgraduate qualifications include not only a master’s degree in any field but also professional degrees such as MBBS, Engineering or Technology degrees, Law degrees, Chartered Accountant qualifications, or a PG Diploma (of one or two years) from an accredited institution or university.</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-ddac097780514933976c9c76a872ad63"><strong>Age Limit for Punjab Good Governance Fellowship Programme 2025:</strong></p>



<p class="">Up to 35 years at the time of application.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-122f504c0a772f23305d15cbeeb8f680"><strong>Steps of Application Process:</strong></p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li class="">Round 1: MCQ Assessment</li>



<li class="">Round 2: Essay Assessment</li>



<li class="">Round 3: Essay Submission</li>



<li class="">Interview Round I</li>



<li class="">Interview Round II</li>
</ul>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-4b33c59bb8ff404c8fb1b2967018afd6"><strong> Punjab Good Governance Fellowship Remuneration:</strong></p>



<p class="">1.20 lakhs per month all inclusive.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-7cebecbb45c58626f09147979c789dcf"><strong>Punjab Good Governance Fellowship Duration:</strong></p>



<p class="">2 Years</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-34164a02cd8b1d670a9cb5bf224165e3"><strong>Last Dates of Punjab Good Governance Fellowship:</strong></p>



<p class="">Registration Deadline: 30 May 25, 11:59 PM</p>



<p class="has-vivid-red-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-c1ce9bae1af0fe1d4a2184cf114782bd"><strong>Details about Punjab Good Governance Fellowship: <a href="https://unstop.com/p/punjab-good-governance-fellowship-programme-2025-1478876?ref=UVN98WIT" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="">Click Here</a></strong></p>



<p class="has-vivid-red-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-c8e700179cb8017345a8418569ab0902"><strong>How to Register for Punjab Good Governance Fellowship</strong>: <strong><a href="https://unstop.com/competitions/1478876/register" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="">Click Here</a></strong></p>



<p class=""></p><p>The post <a href="https://applyfornaukri.com/punjab-good-governance-fellowship-programme-2025/">Punjab Good Governance Fellowship Programme 2025</a> first appeared on <a href="https://applyfornaukri.com">Apply For Naukri</a>.</p>]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
