					<description><![CDATA[<p>Online Application for Office Assistant (Peon) Recruitment in Bank of Baroda Advt. No. BOB/HRM/REC/ADVT/2025/05 About Bank of Baroda Office Assistant</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://applyfornaukri.com/office-assistant-peon-recruitment-in-bank-of-baroda/">Office Assistant (Peon) Recruitment in Bank of Baroda</a> first appeared on <a href="https://applyfornaukri.com">Apply For Naukri</a>.</p>]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class="has-text-align-center has-background has-medium-font-size" style="background-color:#e9a1a1"><strong>Online Application for Office Assistant (Peon) Recruitment in Bank of Baroda</strong></p>



<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized"><img decoding="async" width="316" height="78" src="https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Screenshot-2025-05-10-194947.jpg?fit=316%2C78&amp;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-11163" style="width:316px;height:auto" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Screenshot-2025-05-10-194947.jpg?w=316&amp;ssl=1 316w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Screenshot-2025-05-10-194947.jpg?resize=300%2C74&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Screenshot-2025-05-10-194947.jpg?resize=150%2C37&amp;ssl=1 150w" sizes="(max-width: 316px) 100vw, 316px" /></figure>



<p class="has-text-align-center has-light-green-cyan-background-color has-background has-medium-font-size"><strong>Advt. No. BOB/HRM/REC/ADVT/2025/05</strong></p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-cef923a83de6591cc2083a6234dba36e"><strong>About Bank of Baroda Office Assistant (Peon) Vacancy:</strong></p>



<p class="">Bank of Baroda is inviting application for the post of Office Assistant (Peon). 10th (Highschool) Pass candidates can apply online before 23.05.2025. </p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-a05a9484d9968dbc419168bcdb29bfef"><strong>Post Name, No, of Post and Qualification:</strong> </p>



<figure class="wp-block-table"><table class="has-background" style="background-color:#c6d6e4"><tbody><tr><td><strong>Post Name</strong></td><td><strong>No. of Post</strong></td><td><strong>Qualification</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Office Assistant (Peon)</td><td>500</td><td>1. Passed the 10th Standard (S.S.C./ Matriculation)<br>2. Proficient in the Local Language of the State/ Union Territories</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-0d3e5afa726a7b749b41d99e288534f2"><strong>Age Limit for Office Assistant (Peon) Vacancy:</strong> </p>



<p class="">Minimum: 18 years Maximum: 26 years.  Age relaxation as per BOB Rules.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-d786d20fc66400049b6e94bca33fbf4c"><strong>Scale of Pay:</strong></p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="823" height="69" src="https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image.png?fit=823%2C69&amp;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-11164" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image.png?w=823&amp;ssl=1 823w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image.png?resize=300%2C25&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image.png?resize=768%2C64&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image.png?resize=150%2C13&amp;ssl=1 150w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /></figure>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-c6b1b4573af21d9d8ed6668b31040beb"><strong>Application Fee of Bank of Baroda Office Assistant (Peon) Vacancy:</strong></p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li class="">Rs.600/- + Applicable Taxes + Payment Gateway Charges for General, EWS &amp; OBC candidates</li>



<li class="">Rs.100/- + Applicable Taxes + Payment Gateway Charges for SC, ST, PwBD, EXS, DISXS &amp; Women candidates</li>
</ul>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-d3541fd918e3c287c09d68bd97ee88de"><strong>Pre-Examination/ Recruitment Training:</strong></p>



<p class="">The Bank arranges pre-examination training for SC/ST/OBC/PWD candidates, free of cost, in online mode. Candidates belonging to SC/ST/OBC/PWD, who desire to avail of the pre-examination training, should invariably fill in the details in the relevant column while filling the ON-LINE application.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-a23d071d96699fd4b958ed7c5e6392d2"><strong>Bank of Baroda Office Assistant (Peon):</strong></p>



<p class="">Online test followed by Local Vernacular Language Test (Language Proficiency Test) of candidates, qualifying/ passing in the online test.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-9d63a8c51a35cd795b3b8de2c9b9c5a8"><strong>Important Dates:</strong></p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li class="">Online Registration of Application starts from : 03.05.2025</li>



<li class="">Last date for Submission of Application &amp; Payment of fees: 23.05.2025</li>
</ul>



<p class="has-vivid-red-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-fc6249744691d08c6e6ff018c256edf3"><strong>Download Bank of Baroda Office Assistant (Peon) Vacancy Notification:</strong> <strong><a href="https://www.bankofbaroda.in/-/media/Project/BOB/CountryWebsites/India/Career/2025/25-04/Advertisment-02-36.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="">Click Here</a></strong></p>



<p class="has-vivid-red-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-e72434ef243cee9a68020f7a99063d33"><strong>How to Apply for Bank of Baroda Office Assistant (Peon) Vacancy:</strong> <strong><a href="https://ibpsonline.ibps.in/bobapr25/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="">Click Here</a></strong></p>



<p class="">Note: Above details are for only reference, see complete notification of vacanacy.</p><p>The post <a href="https://applyfornaukri.com/office-assistant-peon-recruitment-in-bank-of-baroda/">Office Assistant (Peon) Recruitment in Bank of Baroda</a> first appeared on <a href="https://applyfornaukri.com">Apply For Naukri</a>.</p>]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
