					<description><![CDATA[<p>Online Application for Experienced Executive (Hospital Administration) in NTPC Limited About Experienced Executive (Hospital Administration) in NTPC: NTPC Limited, India&#8217;s</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://applyfornaukri.com/recruitment-of-hospital-administration-executive-in-ntpc/">Recruitment of Hospital Administration Executive in NTPC</a> first appeared on <a href="https://applyfornaukri.com">Apply For Naukri</a>.</p>]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class="has-text-align-center has-black-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-1efd678c85fa8ab34c67ad4c77dac6f8" style="background-color:#fa6d6d"><strong>Online Application for Experienced Executive (Hospital Administration) in NTPC Limited</strong></p>



<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized"><img data-recalc-dims="1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="800" height="444" src="https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/NTPC-Limited-3.jpg?resize=800%2C444&#038;ssl=1" alt="Executive (Hospital Administration)" class="wp-image-5536" style="width:401px;height:auto" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/NTPC-Limited-3.jpg?w=900&amp;ssl=1 900w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/NTPC-Limited-3.jpg?resize=300%2C167&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/NTPC-Limited-3.jpg?resize=768%2C427&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/NTPC-Limited-3.jpg?resize=800%2C445&amp;ssl=1 800w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/NTPC-Limited-3.jpg?resize=150%2C83&amp;ssl=1 150w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /></figure>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-c91dd0746d78513bb82da8c0f12d107e"><strong>About Experienced Executive (Hospital Administration) in NTPC:</strong></p>



<p class="">NTPC Limited, India&#8217;s largest integrated energy company, is driving the nation&#8217;s progress with an installed capacity of 79,930 MW and a strong presence across the entire power generation value chain. NTPC is looking for experienced professionals on fixed term basis. </p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-f039629e9c584f18d31bf03f1c54d734"><strong>Post Name, No. of Post, Qualification and Experience:</strong></p>



<figure class="wp-block-table"><table class="has-background" style="background-color:#c3ced8"><tbody><tr><td><strong>Post Name</strong></td><td><strong>No. of Post</strong></td><td><strong>Qualification</strong></td><td><strong>Experience</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>Executive (Hospital Administration)</strong></td><td>UR-08<br>EWS-01<br>OBC-03<br>SC-02<br>ST-01<br>Total-15</td><td>A graduate degree in Hospital Administration’ Hospital Management <br><strong>OR</strong> a graduate degree along with a Diploma/PG Diploma/PG Degree in Hospital Administration/Hospital Management</td><td>1 Year </td></tr></tbody></table></figure>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-8981150e4a58ea8ad11508e96a42bc97"><strong>Age Limit for Recruitment of Hospital Administration Executive in NTPC:</strong></p>



<p class="">45 Years ( Age relaxation as per NTPC rules)</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-df8b7d165349a5423c2d54d42e5b2af4"><strong>Tenure of Engagement:</strong></p>



<p class="">3 years extendable up to 5 years.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-3b024e17cf0c9eba343d974c6135d1b7"><strong>Remuneration:</strong></p>



<p class="">Monthly Consolidated amount of Rs. 71,000/-. Additionally, Company Accommodation/HRA, Retention benefit and Medical facility for self, spouse, dependent parents and two children.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-4c0bf6747a203d0cc341dac83f33de60"><strong>Application Fee:</strong></p>



<p class="">General/EWS/OBC &#8211; Rs. 300/-. SC/ST/PWBD/XSM category &amp; female candidates need not pay the application fee.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-9d63a8c51a35cd795b3b8de2c9b9c5a8"><strong>Important Dates:</strong></p>



<p class=""><strong>Commencement of online application:</strong> 11.04.2025<br><strong>Last date for online application:</strong> 25.04.2025</p>



<p class="has-vivid-red-color has-text-color has-medium-font-size"><strong>Download NTPC Hospital Administration Executive vacancy Notification:</strong> <strong><a href="https://careers.ntpc.co.in/recruitment/advertisements/07_25_eng_adv" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="">Click Here</a></strong></p>



<p class="has-vivid-red-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-3928dcd4411f63c5202c96f8643c8421"><strong>How to Apply for NTPC Hospital Administration Executive Vacancy:</strong> <strong><a href="https://careers.ntpc.co.in/recruitment/login.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="">Click Here</a></strong></p><p>The post <a href="https://applyfornaukri.com/recruitment-of-hospital-administration-executive-in-ntpc/">Recruitment of Hospital Administration Executive in NTPC</a> first appeared on <a href="https://applyfornaukri.com">Apply For Naukri</a>.</p>]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
