<p>The post <a href="https://applyfornaukri.com/young-professional-vacancies-in-office-of-cmd-and-corporate-planning-of-seci/">Young Professional Vacancies in office of C&MD and Corporate Planning of SECI</a> first appeared on <a href="https://applyfornaukri.com">Apply For Naukri</a>.</p>]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class="has-text-align-center has-black-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-1b2db1a4a8d1e9a38d508bdae2b73a29" style="background-color:#ec5c5c"><strong>Online Application for Young Professional Vacancies in office of C&amp;MD and Corporate Planning of SECI</strong></p>



<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized"><img data-recalc-dims="1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="285" height="177" src="https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/SECI.png?resize=285%2C177&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-5963" style="width:401px;height:auto" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/SECI.png?w=285&amp;ssl=1 285w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/SECI.png?resize=150%2C93&amp;ssl=1 150w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 285px) 100vw, 285px" /></figure>



<p class="has-text-align-center has-black-color has-cyan-bluish-gray-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-b7c96809b3987c731920da96de5cbc70"><strong>NOTIFICATION NO: 02/2025</strong></p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-d2020e8602ea055ea8197de3fe2ebdb0"><strong>About SECI and Young Professional Vacancies:</strong></p>



<p class="">Solar Energy Corporation of India Ltd. (SECI) is a NAVRATNA schedule ‘A’ CPSE under the administrative jurisdiction of the Ministry of New and Renewable Energy. SECI invites applications for various positions of Young Professional on contractual basis from talented, innovative and dynamic candidates who are keen to demonstrate their proven academic, credential, professional achievements. </p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-28431af92dd22dfe56a02722bf48a840"><strong>Post Name, No. of Post and Qualification:</strong></p>



<figure class="wp-block-table"><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>Post Name</strong></td><td><strong>No. of Post</strong></td><td><strong>Qualification</strong></td><td><strong>Experience</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Young Professional <br>(Office of C&amp;MD)</td><td>01</td><td>(a) Bachelor of Engineering/ B. Tech OR<br>(b) Masters in Science / Technology/ Computer<br>Application/ Commerce/ Statistics/ Maths/ Economics/<br>Management / Communication Development / Post<br>Graduate Diploma in Management including that of<br>one year Executive Post Graduate Programme</td><td>03 Years</td></tr><tr><td>Young Professional <br>(Corporate Planning)</td><td>01</td><td>(a) B. Tech in any discipline and<br>(b) MBA/PGDM (Finance or any combination thereof,<br>Power Management/ Strategic Management/ Corporate<br>Strategy) with minimum 60% marks or equivalent CGPA<br>from recognized University/ Institutes.</td><td>03</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-b4c4cb65c97e7e79af3d85fb68368930"><strong>Age Limit for SECI Young Professional Vacancies:</strong></p>



<p class="">Not exceeding 30 years on the date of closing of advertisement.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-41f3c6ed26f661ee285e75e11e11faae"><strong>Remuneration:</strong> </p>



<p class="">Rs. 70,000/- per month for first year, Rs. 75,000/- per month for second year, and Rs. 80,000/- per month for third year.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-255f509ef714881f365e5963ca8bb849"><strong>Selection Process:</strong></p>



<p class="">Application Shortlisting and Written Test / GD / Interview.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-bf35c5e97f42fe3db0682c8dfbf43ca2"><strong>Period of Induction:</strong></p>



<p class="">The induction period is suggested to last for a minimum of one year and a maximum of three years.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-9d63a8c51a35cd795b3b8de2c9b9c5a8"><strong>Important Dates:</strong></p>



<p class="">Application Start Date: 16-March-2025, 11:00 Hrs</p>



<p class="">Application End Date: 15-Apr-2025, 17:00 Hrs</p>



<p class="has-vivid-red-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-248862326b6d07abeb50f4324df89fa8"><strong>Download SECI Young Professional Vacancy Notification:</strong> <strong><a href="https://www.seci.co.in/Upload/JobDesc/638777190856678947.pdf">Click Here</a></strong></p>



<p class="has-vivid-red-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-828457374ca7325d499b7ce4ef804525"><strong>How to Apply for SECI Young Professional Vacancy:</strong> <strong><a href="https://www.seci.co.in/view-job-apply">Click Here</a></strong></p>



<p class="">Note: All the above content is for information purpose. Please see advertisement for complete information.  </p><p>The post <a href="https://applyfornaukri.com/young-professional-vacancies-in-office-of-cmd-and-corporate-planning-of-seci/">Young Professional Vacancies in office of C&MD and Corporate Planning of SECI</a> first appeared on <a href="https://applyfornaukri.com">Apply For Naukri</a>.</p>]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
