<p>The post <a href="https://applyfornaukri.com/recruitment-of-agriculture-graduate-trainee-agt-in-iffco-2025/">Recruitment of Agriculture Graduate Trainee (AGT) in IFFCO 2025</a> first appeared on <a href="https://applyfornaukri.com">Apply For Naukri</a>.</p>]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class="has-text-align-center has-black-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-4e97aa522b22ec73c233f8f8cbbb4e2b" style="background-color:#f17d7d"><strong>Online Application for Agriculture Graduate Trainee (AGT) in IFFCO 2025</strong></p>



<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-large is-resized"><img data-recalc-dims="1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="800" height="450" src="https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/iffco-1.jpg?resize=800%2C450&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-11140" style="width:412px;height:auto" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/iffco-1.jpg?resize=1024%2C576&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/iffco-1.jpg?resize=300%2C169&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/iffco-1.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/iffco-1.jpg?resize=150%2C84&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/iffco-1.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /></figure>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-fd0d8eb477f6649379c3d69fa76f5d87"><strong>About IFFCO AGT 2025 Vacancies:</strong></p>



<p class="">Indian Farmers Fertiliser Cooperative Limited, also known as IFFCO, is a multi-state cooperative society engaged in the manufacture and marketing of fertiliser. IFFCO is invited online application for Agriculture Graduate Trainee (AGT). Last date of online application for IFFCO AGT is 15.03.2025.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-2dd31a7d90fc6cbe3283cc5094016cc5"><strong>Post Name and Qualification:</strong></p>



<figure class="wp-block-table"><table class="has-background has-fixed-layout" style="background-color:#b8c9d8"><tbody><tr><td><strong>Post Name</strong></td><td><strong>Qualification</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Agriculture Graduate Trainee (AGT)</td><td>Four Years B.Sc. (Agriculture) Full Time Regular Degree.<br>General/OBC with 60% and SC/ST candidates 55% marks.<br><em>The candidates who have passed B.Sc. (Agriculture) degree in the year 2022 and thereafter can only apply.</em></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-baae119158b3dc4b8c0b352106b14450"><strong>Age Limit for IFFCO AGT Vacancy:</strong></p>



<p class="">30 years, as on 01st March, 2025. (Relaxable by 5 years for SCs/STs &amp; by 3 years for OBCs not belonging to creamy layer)</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-509dc4d3d67d001448346db107e01a82"><strong>Compensation:</strong></p>



<p class="">Presently the stipend is Rs. 33,300/- p.m. </p>



<p class="">On successful completion of one year’s training and subject to requirement of IFFCO, the AGTs may be absorbed at the basic pay of Rs.37000/- p.m. in the regular Pay Scale of Rs.37000-70000, and allowances/ benefits as per rules of the IFFCO.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-c6933c1c0c392548cdc1edc8e9267fd4"><strong>Locations of Posting:</strong></p>



<p class="">For Field Offices located all over India</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-1dbebd4638fe348f30d09e46db300dd7"><strong>Selection  Process of IFFCO AGT:</strong></p>



<ol class="wp-block-list">
<li class="">Preliminary Computer Based On-Line Test</li>



<li class="">Final On-Line Test</li>



<li class="">Personal Interview </li>
</ol>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-2fd91dcea852f55fc205a60d421eba86"><strong>Medical Examination of IFFCO AGT:</strong></p>



<p class="">Candidates short-listed after Personal Interview will be medically examined as per IFFCO’s medical standards before final selection.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-6468bda3ddf7c1fe0b311e0d0cf7df87"><strong>IFFCO AGT Final Online test Centres:</strong></p>



<p class="">Ahmedabad, Bengaluru, Delhi, Kolkata, Chennai, Lucknow, Nagpur, Guwahati, Patna, Raipur, Surat, Varanasi, Chandigarh, Dehradun, Pune, Hyderabad, Vijayawada, Cochin, Jodhpur, Jammu, Shimla, Bhopal, Jabalpur.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-8ce7ba7821010ae3fa70c2c31f7d45fe"><strong>Last date of IFFCO AGT Application:</strong></p>



<p class="">15/03/2025</p>



<p class="has-vivid-red-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-769fe7d53211b81afa908e19160c3792"><strong>Download Notification of Agriculture Graduate Trainee (AGT) in IFFCO:</strong> <strong><a href="https://iffco-public-assets.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/s3fs-public/2025-02/Vacancy-advt-for-the-post-of-AGT.pdf">Click Here</a></strong></p>



<p class="has-vivid-red-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-292cc4dc637b8d7ea7da142bdb9bd301"><strong>How to Apply for IFFCO AGT Vacancy:</strong> <strong><a href="https://agt.iffco.in/LOGIN-2/iffcoagt.jsp">Click Here</a></strong></p>



<p class="">Note: Content of this website if for information purpose only. </p><p>The post <a href="https://applyfornaukri.com/recruitment-of-agriculture-graduate-trainee-agt-in-iffco-2025/">Recruitment of Agriculture Graduate Trainee (AGT) in IFFCO 2025</a> first appeared on <a href="https://applyfornaukri.com">Apply For Naukri</a>.</p>]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
