<p class="">NTPC Limited is India&#8217;s largest integrated energy company with installed capacity of 77,393 MW and has presence in the entire value chain of the power generation business. Commensurate with our country&#8217;s growth challenges, NTPC has embarked upon an ambitious plan to attain a total installed capacity of 130 GW by 2032. NTPC is looking for Assistant Executive (Operations) on Fixed Term Basis. Last Date of online Application is 01.03.2025.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-48fd615c5ff374f9ac6aa2b696194419"><strong>Post Name, No. of Vacancies and Qualification:</strong></p>



