<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-c5a15a2583d701a2816034f35fe8aff0"><strong>Upper Age Limit for NTPC Assistant Executive (Operations):</strong></p>



<p class="">35 Years (Upper Age Limit as per Rules).</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-423c2b28653e62b61c63890b1c978404"><strong>Tenure of Engagement:</strong> </p>



<p class="">Fixed Term Employment of 3 Years ( 2 Years Extendable).</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-e30e1d5b7961008874f17c709e361c7a"><strong>Remunerations of NTPC Assistant Executive (Operations):</strong></p>



<p class="">Fixed Monthly amount of Rs. 55000/- and HRA or Accommodation, Night Shift Allowance and Medical Facility for Family.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-80780d263ed8dc2b1ca769cb0673e212"><strong>NTPC Assistant Executive (Operations) Application Fee:</strong></p>



<p class=""> Rs. 300/- (SC/ST/PwBD/XSM category and Female Candidates are not to pay application fee)</p>



