					<description><![CDATA[<p>Online Application for Junior Court Assistant in Supreme Court of India About Junior Court Assistant Vacancies in Supreme Court of</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://applyfornaukri.com/junior-court-assistant-vacancies-in-supreme-court-of-india/">Junior Court Assistant Vacancies in Supreme Court of India</a> first appeared on <a href="https://applyfornaukri.com">Apply For Naukri</a>.</p>]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class="has-text-align-center has-black-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-07554f9f85547a94e044f8665e4b4242" style="background-color:#f15959"><strong>Online Application for Junior Court Assistant in Supreme Court of India</strong></p>



<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized"><img data-recalc-dims="1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="769" height="514" src="https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/supreme-court.png?resize=769%2C514&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-7137" style="width:521px;height:auto" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/supreme-court.png?w=769&amp;ssl=1 769w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/supreme-court.png?resize=300%2C201&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/supreme-court.png?resize=150%2C100&amp;ssl=1 150w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 769px) 100vw, 769px" /></figure>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-7903325718d49efeb44b20c780c8d206"><strong>About Junior Court Assistant Vacancies in Supreme Court of India:</strong></p>



<p class="">Supreme Court of India Inviting online Application for filling up of 241 vacancies from Graduate Candidates. Last Date of application is 8 Mar 2025 (11:55 PM). </p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-c650fd2d5ce9d408fc3fcba2de1e94ff"><strong>Post Name, No. of Post and Qualification: </strong></p>



<figure class="wp-block-table"><table class="has-background" style="background-color:#c9dae9"><tbody><tr><td><strong>Post Name</strong></td><td><strong>No. of Post</strong></td><td><strong>Qualification</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Junior Court Assistant</td><td>241</td><td>Bachelor’s degree of a recognized University<br>Minimum speed of 35 w.p.m. in English Typing on Computer<br>Knowledge of Computer operation</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-66fae8559243a0ab6ca917c06997ee10"><strong>Age Limit for Junior Court Assistant Vacancies in Supreme Court of India:</strong></p>



<p class="">Candidates should not be below 18 years and above 30 years of age as on 08.03.2025. Age relaxation as per Govt. Rules.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-4edb2c430217712b22bb94dc0a7ff8aa"><strong>Salary of Junior Court Assistant in Supreme Court of India:</strong></p>



<p class="">Level 6 of Pay Matrix with initial Basic Pay of Rs. 35,400/-. The approximate Gross Salary as per existing rate of allowances including HRA comes to Rs. 72,040/- per month (pre-revised pay scale PB-2 with Grade Pay of Rs. 4200/-). </p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-1ad562da24dd3e22bc0dca0e5f7384b0"><strong>Application Fee of Junior Court Assistant in Supreme Court of India:</strong></p>



<p class="">Rs. 1000/- for General/OBC candidates and Rs. 250/- for SC/ST/Ex-Servicemen/Differently Abled/Freedom Fighter candidates.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-9d63a8c51a35cd795b3b8de2c9b9c5a8"><strong>Important Dates:</strong></p>



<p class="">Online registration of application is 05.02.2025 at 10.00 A.M.<br>Last date thereof is 08.03.2025 at 23.55 P.M.</p>



