<p>The post <a href="https://applyfornaukri.com/junior-executive-fire-hr-and-official-language-in-airport-authority-of-india/">Junior Executive ( Fire, HR and Official Language) in Airport Authority of India</a> first appeared on <a href="https://applyfornaukri.com">Apply For Naukri</a>.</p>]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class="has-text-align-center has-black-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-efd07ed3a9b5a56d5068242ee3c60960" style="background-color:#f16565"><strong>Online Application for Junior Executive ( Fire Services, HR and Official Language) in Airport of India </strong></p>



<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized"><img data-recalc-dims="1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="800" height="400" src="https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/AAI_Recruitment_2023_Young-Professional.jpg?resize=800%2C400&#038;ssl=1" alt="Junior Executive Vacancy 2025" class="wp-image-5664" style="width:805px;height:auto" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/AAI_Recruitment_2023_Young-Professional.jpg?w=860&amp;ssl=1 860w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/AAI_Recruitment_2023_Young-Professional.jpg?resize=300%2C150&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/AAI_Recruitment_2023_Young-Professional.jpg?resize=768%2C384&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/AAI_Recruitment_2023_Young-Professional.jpg?resize=150%2C75&amp;ssl=1 150w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Junior Executive </figcaption></figure>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-5688c3ee55f9a1c5692e4aec2ef3b8c2"><strong>About Junior Executive Vacancies in Airport Authority of India:</strong></p>



<p class="">Airports Authority of India (AAI), a Government of India Public Sector Enterprise, constituted by an Act of Parliament, is entrusted with the responsibility of creating, upgrading, maintaining and managing civil aviation infrastructure both on the ground and air space in the country. AAI inviting application for Junior Executives. Application open from 17.02.2025 to 18.03.2025.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-cb3f86062557e280ad2f319f930cfabc"><strong>Post Name, No. of Posts and Qualification:</strong></p>



<figure class="wp-block-table"><table class="has-background" style="background-color:#d2deea"><tbody><tr><td><strong>Post Name</strong></td><td><strong>No. of Post</strong></td><td><strong>Qualification</strong></td><td><strong>Experience</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Junior Executive <br>(Fire Services)</td><td>13</td><td>Bachelor’s Degree in Engineering. /Tech. in Fire<br>Engg./Mechanical Engg./Automobile Engg.</td><td>No experience</td></tr><tr><td>Junior Executive<br>(Human Resources)</td><td>66</td><td>Graduate and MBA or equivalent (2 years’ duration)<br>with specialization in HRM/HRD/PM&amp;IR/Labour<br>Welfare.</td><td>No experience</td></tr><tr><td>Junior Executive <br>(Official Language)</td><td>04</td><td>Post-Graduation in Hindi or in English with English or<br>Hindi respectively as a Subject at Degree Level or<br>Post-Graduation in any other subject with Hindi and<br>English as compulsory / elective subject at Degree<br>Level.</td><td>Experience of two years in<br>Translation relating to<br>Glossary and from English <br>to Hindi and Hindi<br>to English preferably of<br>Technical or Scientific literature.</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-29be3cf8ae62dff76e2bb9526c9adabd"><strong>Age Limit for Junior Executive Vacancy in AAI:</strong></p>



<p class="">Maximum age 27 years as on 18.03.2025. Age relaxation as per AAI rules. (See notification)</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-63c60129a1766f521fc7e916b2cf6c27"><strong>Pay Scale of AAI Junior Executive:</strong></p>



<p class="">Junior Executive [Group-B: E-1 level] : Rs.40000 &#8211; 3% &#8211; 140000. Approximate CTC for the post of Junior Executive would be Rs. 13 lakhs per annum.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-d4e02ca199a0537967337666c6df4fcd"><strong>Selection Process of AAI Junior Executive:</strong></p>



<p class="">Computer Based Test will be followed by Application Verification/ Subsequent Tests, as applicable for the posts. For the post Junior Executive (Fire Services), Application Verification will be followed by Physical Measurement Test, Driving Test and Physical Endurance Test.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-6dc9545708a5ba5883a385c1e62bd7c4"><strong>AAI Junior Executive Vacancy Application Fee:</strong></p>



<p class="">Application Fee of Rs.1000/- . However, the SC/ST/PWD candidates/ Apprentices who have successfully completed one year of Apprenticeship Training in AAI/ Female candidates are exempted from payment of Fee.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-8fdc59f069c48e77921940c3288e4c6f"><strong>Important Date of AAI Junior Executive Vacancies:</strong></p>



<p class="">Opening date for On-line Applications 17.02.2025<br>Closing date for On-line Applications 18.03.2025<br>Tentative Date of Computer Based Test Will be announced on AAI Website</p>



<p class="has-vivid-red-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-cbd6c2253c0688ae8db7ef65e8c05ac6"><strong>Download Notification of AAI Junior Executive Vacancy 2025:</strong> <strong><a href="https://www.aai.aero/sites/default/files/examdashboard_advertisement/Detailed%20Advertisement%2001-2025-CHQ_0.pdf">Click Here</a></strong></p>



<p class="has-vivid-red-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-d246adfb92c537b9d43c6c188a46c187"><strong>How to Apply for AAI Junior Executive Vacancies:</strong> <strong><a href="https://www.aai.aero/en/careers/recruitment">Click Here</a></strong></p><p>The post <a href="https://applyfornaukri.com/junior-executive-fire-hr-and-official-language-in-airport-authority-of-india/">Junior Executive ( Fire, HR and Official Language) in Airport Authority of India</a> first appeared on <a href="https://applyfornaukri.com">Apply For Naukri</a>.</p>]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
