										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class="has-text-align-center has-black-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-f1468915e0b060ad25d4b4aa5a24607f" style="background-color:#ec7272"><strong>Online Application for 55 Management Trainee in Agriculture Insurance Company of India Limited (AIC) 2025</strong></p>



