										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class="has-text-align-center has-black-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-081124da8d23020ed5add8eb7dfd50c7" style="background-color:#eb7777"><strong>Online Application for Court Master, Senior Personal Assistant and Personal Assistant Recruitment in Supreme Court of India</strong></p>



<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized"><img data-recalc-dims="1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="769" height="514" src="https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/supreme-court.png?resize=769%2C514&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-7137" style="width:575px;height:auto" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/supreme-court.png?w=769&amp;ssl=1 769w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/supreme-court.png?resize=300%2C201&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/supreme-court.png?resize=150%2C100&amp;ssl=1 150w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 769px) 100vw, 769px" /></figure>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-29cf34fb2d8560f1a338ac7e99d5677e"><strong>About Supreme Court of India Vacancies:</strong></p>



<p class="">Supreme Court of India inviting application for Court Master (Shorthand) (Group-A Gazetted Post), Senior Personal Assistant and Personal Assistant (Group &#8216;B&#8217;, Non-Gazetted Posts). Last date of application is 25.12.2024 at 23:55 hours.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-cb3f86062557e280ad2f319f930cfabc"><strong>Post Name, No. of Posts and Qualification:</strong></p>



<figure class="wp-block-table"><table class="has-background" style="background-color:#c0c9d3"><tbody><tr><td><strong>Post Name</strong></td><td><strong>No. of Post</strong></td><td><strong>Qualification</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Court Master (Shorthand)</td><td>31</td><td>1) A Degree in Law of a recognized University in India.<br>2) Proficiency in Shorthand (English) with a speed of 120 w.p.m.<br>3) Knowledge of Computer Operation with a typing speed of 40 w.p.m.<br><strong>Experience</strong>:- Minimum 5 years’ regular service</td></tr><tr><td>Senior Personal Assistant</td><td>33</td><td>1) Degree of a recognized University.<br>2) Proficiency in Shorthand (English) with a speed of 110 w.p.m.<br>3) Knowledge of Computer Operation with a typing speed of 40 w.p.m.</td></tr><tr><td>Personal Assistant</td><td>43</td><td>1) Degree of a recognized University.<br>2) Proficiency in Shorthand (English) with a speed of 100 w.p.m.<br>3) Knowledge of Computer Operation with a typing speed of 40 w.p.m.</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-11816857d7e3873381a9c45e8604ec2b"><strong>Age Limit of Vacancies in Supreme Court of India:</strong></p>



<ol class="wp-block-list">
<li class="">Court Master (Shorthand): 30 to 45 years</li>



<li class="">Senior Personal Assistant: 18 to 30 years</li>



<li class="">Personal Assistant: 18 to 30 years</li>



<li class="">Upper Age relaxations as per Rules</li>
</ol>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-f39a8aee9185b926602fde712d4969e0"><strong>Salary in Supreme Court of India:</strong></p>



<ol class="wp-block-list">
<li class="">Court Master (Shorthand): Basic Pay of Rs. 67,700 (Level-11)</li>



<li class="">Senior Personal Assistant: Basic Pay of Rs. 47,600 (Level-8)</li>



<li class="">Personal Assistant: Basic Pay of Rs. 44,900 (Level-7)</li>
</ol>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-dc156c6cc599310744a7e8158bfb9fad"><strong>Application Fee for Supreme Court of India Vacancies:</strong></p>



<ol class="wp-block-list">
<li class="">General/OBC candidates: Rs.1,000/-</li>



<li class="">SC/ST/Ex-Servicemen/PH candidates/Dependents of Freedom Fighters: Rs. 250/-</li>
</ol>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-11bf6b4ac137b909db0d6d248821affb"><strong>Examination Center:</strong></p>



<p class="">Ahmedabad, Ambala, Bengaluru, Bhopal, Bhubaneswar, Chennai, Delhi, Ernakulam, Guwahati, Hyderabad, Jabalpur, Jaipur, Kanpur, Kolkata,<br>Lucknow, Mumbai, Mysuru (Mysore), Nagpur, Patna, Prayagraj, Pune, Udaipur, and Visakhapatnam.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-3918acd8f4506f7e602ac01224cf417c"><strong>Important dates:</strong></p>



<p class="">The starting date for online registration of application is 04.12.2024 and last date thereof is 25.12.2024 at 23:55 hours.</p>



