										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class="has-text-align-center has-black-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-62f8d37eee4f56cbd571e90c762f4eb8" style="background-color:#f35f5f"><strong>Online Application for the post of Fixed Tenure Engineers for BEL Bangalore Complex and other Project sites</strong></p>



<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-large is-resized"><img data-recalc-dims="1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="800" height="420" src="https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BEL.jpg?resize=800%2C420&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-5741" style="width:558px;height:auto" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BEL.jpg?resize=1024%2C538&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BEL.jpg?resize=300%2C158&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BEL.jpg?resize=768%2C403&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BEL.jpg?resize=390%2C205&amp;ssl=1 390w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BEL.jpg?resize=150%2C79&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BEL.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /></figure>



<p class="has-text-align-center has-black-color has-light-green-cyan-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-75d12e133d964fc21aa8aa6663dfbd24"><strong>Advt No.383/HR/FTE/24-25</strong></p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-8b45c25279b3faaf3eb1dde77c540335"><strong>About Fixed Tenure Engineers Vacancy in Bharat Electronics Limited:</strong></p>



<p class="">The following engineers are needed on a fixed-tenure basis for a term of five years (extension possible for up to two years) by Bharat Electronics Limited, the leading professional electronics company in Navaratna and India, for its Bangalore-only complex and other project sites. Last date of application is 10-12-2024.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-abceff7da48f2d02e18d88d8faf24aa2"><strong>Post Name, No. of Post, Qualification:</strong></p>



<figure class="wp-block-table"><table class="has-cyan-bluish-gray-background-color has-background"><tbody><tr><td><strong>Post Name</strong></td><td><strong>No. of Post and Discipline</strong></td><td><strong>Qualification</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Fixed Tenure Engineer</td><td>UR-99<br>EWS-20<br>OBC-61<br>SC-32<br>ST-17</td><td>BE/B.Tech/B.Sc Engineering (4 years course) from recognised Institute/University/<br>College in the following Engineering disciplines &#8211; Electronics / Mechanical / Computer Science/Electrical Engineering.<br><br><em>UR/ OBC (NCL) / EWS candidates: 60%<br>SC / ST / PwBD candidates: Pass</em></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-aef9469be29eb53fa05e7945558e9752"><strong>Age Limit for BEL Fixed Tenure Engineers Vacancy:</strong></p>



<p class="">Upper age limit (as on 01.11.2024): 28 Years . Relaxation of upper age limit as per BEL rules.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-319c8be258e0405ffb42a104abee2ee7"><strong>Application Fee for BEL Fixed Tenure Engineers Vacancy:</strong></p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li class="">Rs. 400+18% GST i.e Rs.472/-</li>



<li class="">SC / ST / PwBD / Ex-servicemen candidates are exempted from paying application fee.</li>
</ul>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-efe402682e3e2571f9e23f7867f2db4c"><strong>Place of Posting:</strong></p>



<p class="">01- BGFTE01 Bangalore Complex<br>02- EWAFTE02 Ambala, Jodhpur and Batinda<br>03- NSFTE03 Mumbai and Vizag<br>04- SWFTE04 Vizag, Delhi and Indore<br>05- MCFTE05 Ghaziabad</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-e1ecfb2b21bcf604fb234c41485e377e"><strong>Selection Process of BEL Fixed Tenure Engineers Vacancy:</strong></p>



<p class="">Computer Based Test (CBT)</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-fbd27d9bc284cf78f2f71fcddfd60b1d"><strong>Pay and Allowances:</strong> </p>



<p class="">40,000- 3%-1,40,000 and Approx. CTC of Rs.12 Lacs-12.5Lacs.</p>



<p class="">In addition to Basic Pay, other allowance like Dearness Allowance, House Rent Allowance, Conveyance Allowance, Perquisites at the rate of 35% on annual basic pay, Performance related Pay, reimbursement of medical expenses, Group Insurance, PF, Pension, Gratuity(if applicable) etc. as per Company rules.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-b23ec34339cbbfda171b75b04f9bd6af"><strong>Last Date of Application:</strong></p>



<p class="">The last date for applying online is 10-12-2024.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-red-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-1d8f54116459a310068004eaf06c46a0"><strong>Download BEL Fixed Tenure Engineers Vacancy Notification: <a href="https://bel-india.in/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/FTE-Adv-2024-25-English.pdf">Click Here</a></strong></p>



