					<description><![CDATA[<p>Online Application for Junior Assistant Manager (JAM), Grade ‘O’ (2025-26) in IDBI Bank ADVERTISEMENT NO. 10/2024-25 About Junior Assistant Manager</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://applyfornaukri.com/junior-assistant-manager-recruitment-in-idbi-bank/">Junior Assistant Manager Recruitment in IDBI Bank</a> first appeared on <a href="https://applyfornaukri.com">Apply For Naukri</a>.</p>]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class="has-text-align-center has-background has-medium-font-size" style="background-color:#f36262"><strong>Online Application for  Junior Assistant Manager (JAM), Grade ‘O’ (2025-26) in IDBI Bank</strong></p>



<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized"><img data-recalc-dims="1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="800" height="447" src="https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/IDBI-Bank-Executive-Jobs.jpg?resize=800%2C447&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-2497" style="width:615px;height:auto" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/IDBI-Bank-Executive-Jobs.jpg?w=860&amp;ssl=1 860w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/IDBI-Bank-Executive-Jobs.jpg?resize=300%2C167&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/IDBI-Bank-Executive-Jobs.jpg?resize=768%2C429&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/IDBI-Bank-Executive-Jobs.jpg?resize=150%2C84&amp;ssl=1 150w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /></figure>



<p class="has-text-align-center has-black-color has-light-green-cyan-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-70eb42ef6138b18cfa06dd76b248ab17"><strong>ADVERTISEMENT NO. 10/2024-25</strong></p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-52e1b5146a0a38b0f3aea3b39e6ab717">About Junior Assistant Manager (JAM) recruitment in IDBI Bank:</p>



<p class="">IDBI Bank, originally established as the Industrial Development Bank of India in 1964, is a prominent financial institution in India. Initially set up as a wholly owned subsidiary of the Reserve Bank of India, it was later transferred to the Government of India. IDBI is looking for Junior Assistant Manager (JAM), Grade ‘O’ (2025-26). Last Date of Online Application is November 30, 2024.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-table"><table class="has-cyan-bluish-gray-background-color has-background"><tbody><tr><td><strong>Post Name</strong></td><td><strong>No. of Post</strong></td><td><strong>Qualification</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Junior Assistant Manager (JAM)</td><td>500</td><td>Bachelor’s degree in any discipline. Minimum 60% for General, <br>EWS and OBC candidates (55% for SC/ST/PwBD candidates) or <br>equivalent CGPA/OGPA</td></tr><tr><td>JAM- Grade &#8216;O&#8217; (Agri Asset Officer)</td><td>100</td><td>4 years degree ( B.Sc/B Tech/B.E) in Agriculture, Horticulture, Agriculture<br>engineering, Fishery Science/Engineering, Animal Husbandry, Veterinary <br>science, Forestry, Dairy Science/Technology, Food Science/technology, <br>Pisciculture, Agro Forestry, Sericulture<br>Minimum 60% for General, <br>EWS and OBC candidates (55% for SC/ST/PwBD candidates) or <br>equivalent CGPA/OGPA</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-6e095b5b99b8d94fbebc8ee193eb6941"><strong>Age Limit for IDBI Junior Assistant Manager (JAM):</strong></p>



<p class="">Minimum: 20 years ; Maximum: 25 years* . Age Relaxation as per IDBI Rules</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-4118195b4979d820de41c3a28efbaa4b"><strong>Emoluments of Junior Assistant Manager (JAM) in IDBI Bank:</strong></p>



<p class="">Between Rs.6.14 lakh to Rs.6.50 lakh per annum.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-57bb8f89cff73ce816c3ae4c69b8729c"><strong>Selection Process of IDBI Junior Assistant Manager (JAM):</strong></p>



<ol class="wp-block-list">
<li class="">Online test</li>



<li class="">Personal Interview (PI)</li>
</ol>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-ae4627b1e5e9eec5b80664be92c5b89c"><strong>Application Fee for IDBI Junior Assistant Manager (JAM):</strong></p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li class="">Rs.250/- for SC/ST/PwBD candidates ( Only Intimation Charges)</li>



<li class="">Rs.1050/- for all other candidates (Application Fees and Intimation Charges)</li>
</ul>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-e05220b7d761e958b3cc333f90cd7012"><strong>Important Dates of IDBI Junior Assistant Manager (JAM) Recruitment:</strong></p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li class="">Cut-off date for eligibility criteria of Age &amp; Educational Qualification: October 01, 2024</li>



<li class="">Advertisement date November 20, 2024</li>



<li class="">Online Registration and Fee Submission: November 21, 2024 &#8211; November 30, 2024</li>



<li class="">Tentative Online Test (OT)*: December 2024/January 2025</li>
</ul>



<p class="has-vivid-red-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-e2dabf1b0b5f6cba3eb38ba7726a9051"><strong>Download IDBI Junior Assistant Manager (JAM) Recruitment Notification:</strong> <strong><a href="https://www.idbibank.in/pdf/careers/JAM-advertisement-2025-26.pdf">Click Here</a></strong></p>



<p class="has-vivid-red-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-952f31a4ac621d2ed624a08f2860c391"><strong> How to Apply for IDBI Junior Assistant Manager (JAM) Recruitment:</strong> <strong><a href="https://www.idbibank.in/idbi-bank-careers-current-openings.aspx">Click Here</a></strong></p><p>The post <a href="https://applyfornaukri.com/junior-assistant-manager-recruitment-in-idbi-bank/">Junior Assistant Manager Recruitment in IDBI Bank</a> first appeared on <a href="https://applyfornaukri.com">Apply For Naukri</a>.</p>]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
