<p>The post <a href="https://applyfornaukri.com/apprenticeship-training-at-railtel-corporation-of-india-limited/">Apprenticeship Training at RailTel Corporation of India Limited</a> first appeared on <a href="https://applyfornaukri.com">Apply For Naukri</a>.</p>]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class="has-text-align-center has-black-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-efab05c7d12139ed790bbe32945ab49e" style="background-color:#ec4949"><strong>Online Application for Apprenticeship Training at RailTel Corporation of India Limited</strong></p>



<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized"><img data-recalc-dims="1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="650" height="400" src="https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-1.png?resize=650%2C400&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-9783" style="width:449px;height:auto" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-1.png?w=650&amp;ssl=1 650w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-1.png?resize=300%2C185&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-1.png?resize=150%2C92&amp;ssl=1 150w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px" /></figure>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-f3caba916e99de0b8ebc4f7d57cb9eb0"><strong>About Apprenticeship Training at RailTel Corporation of India Limited:</strong></p>



<p class="">Applications are invited from eligible Indian nationals, who meet the eligibility criteria(s) for engagement apprenticeship trainee under the Apprentices Act 1961 {as amended in 1973 and till date) referred herein after as “Act” at RCIL. Last date of application is 30.11.2024.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-6ff635cf3423173e983f868da4daa9d0"><strong>Apprentice Type, Field, Location and No. of Vacancy:</strong></p>



<figure class="wp-block-table"><table class="has-cyan-bluish-gray-background-color has-background"><tbody><tr><td><strong>Apprentices Type</strong></td><td><strong>Field</strong></td><td><strong>State/Location</strong></td><td><strong>Tentative Nos. to be engaged</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Graduate Engineers/<br>Diploma Engineers</td><td>Electronics &amp;<br>Computer Science,<br>{Civil Engg.<br>Electrical &amp;<br>Electronic<br>Engineering</td><td>1.Corporate Office /east<br>Kidwai Nagar, Delhi,<br>Regional Gurgaon office /<br>CNOC<br>2. Regional Offices<br>DLI,, Jaipur, Lucknow,<br>Gorakhpur, Bareilly,<br>Amritsar, Rohtak,<br>Jodhpur, Bikaner, Jaipur,<br>Jhansi, Aligarh, Moradabad,<br>Kanpur, Prayagraj,<br>Ajmer, Agra, Roorkee, Banda,<br>Varanasi, Mau<br>(3) Regional office /<br>|Kolkata, Malda, Asansol,<br>Dhanbad, Sonepur, &amp;<br>Patna, Samastipur,<br>Muzzfarpur, Gaya,<br>Ranchi,.<br>(4) Regional office /<br>Secunderabad, Bangaloore,<br>Chennai, Ernakulam, <br>(5) Western region: Nagpur,<br>Bhopal, Ahmedabad &amp;<br>Mumbai</td><td>40</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-e20f14b1cf69c32439b8bdb40e1079b0">Qualification for <strong>RailTail Apprenticeship:</strong></p>



<p class="">Graduation in Engineering / Technology / Full Time Regular Three Years Diploma in Engineering / Technology ( from Colleges approved by AICTE ) with aggregate 60 % marks in respective stream.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-c7150e2bf8c038344ae22a9d2782bfec"><strong>Monthly Stipend in RailTail Apprenticeship</strong>:</p>



<p class="">14000/- for -Graduate Engineers and 12000/- or Diploma Engineers</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-246db83fa20dc1da72d1eb86d8f96d8e"><strong>Duration of RailTail Apprenticeship:</strong></p>



<p class="">1 (One) Year</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-22b139404935eda0602b3e8fdb12191e"><strong>Age Limit for RailTail Apprenticeship:</strong></p>



<p class="">18-27 years (relaxation for SC/ST/OBC to be as per the Presidential/Governmental Directives) as on date of notification of this letter.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-0bcd8a0f899d217d31aa9d1fbc90f647"><strong>Last Date of RailTail Apprenticeship Application:</strong></p>



<p class="">30.11.2024</p>



<p class="has-vivid-red-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-9c55936a29cf90ca5231a76ef7dcdd2c"><strong>Download Apprenticeship Training  Notification of  RailTel Corporation of India Limited</strong>: <strong><a href="https://www.railtel.in/images/careers/Advertisement%20Notice%20No%20RCIL%202023%20PA%2027%203.pdf">Click Here</a></strong></p>



<p class="has-vivid-red-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-6d37850cf312d3cf1d28f0d690335296"><strong>How to Apply for RailTail Apprenticeship: <a href="https://nats.education.gov.in/index.php">Click Here</a></strong></p>



