					<description><![CDATA[<p>Application for Young Professionals in Ministry of New and Renewable Energy 2024 About Young Professional Vacancy in MNRE: Ministry of</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://applyfornaukri.com/recruitment-of-young-professionals-in-ministry-of-new-and-renewable-energy/">Recruitment of Young Professionals in Ministry of New and Renewable Energy</a> first appeared on <a href="https://applyfornaukri.com">Apply For Naukri</a>.</p>]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class="has-text-align-center has-black-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-35c9b298c257e6bda79914cb19b7e040" style="background-color:#f25656"><strong>Application for Young Professionals in Ministry of New and Renewable Energy 2024</strong> </p>



<figure class="wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-2 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex">
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img data-recalc-dims="1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="345" height="146" data-id="5763" src="https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MNRE.png?resize=345%2C146&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-5763" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MNRE.png?w=345&amp;ssl=1 345w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MNRE.png?resize=300%2C127&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/applyfornaukri.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MNRE.png?resize=150%2C63&amp;ssl=1 150w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 345px) 100vw, 345px" /></figure>
</figure>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-6f219a70dde1cb4d3da33902abe80766"><strong>About Young Professional Vacancy in MNRE:</strong></p>



<p class="">Ministry of New and Renewable Energy (MNRE) invites application for ten (10) positions of Young Professionals from the Young, Talented, Innovative and Dynamic Professionals who are keen to demonstrate their proven academic, credential, professional achievements and leadership qualities. Candidates can submit application within 30 days form advertisement date.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-abceff7da48f2d02e18d88d8faf24aa2"><strong>Post Name, No. of Post, Qualification:</strong></p>



<figure class="wp-block-table"><table class="has-cyan-bluish-gray-background-color has-background"><tbody><tr><td class="has-text-align-center" data-align="center"><strong>No. of Post</strong></td><td><strong>Qualification</strong></td><td><strong>Experience</strong></td></tr><tr><td class="has-text-align-center" data-align="center">5</td><td>Master&#8217;s Degree in Physics/ Chemistry/Mathematics/ Statistics<br><strong>OR</strong><br>B.E/ B.Tech in any stream relevant to Renewable Energy<br><strong>OR</strong><br>2 years PG Diploma in Management, PG Diploma in Power Management <br>Renewable Energy &amp; Grid Interface Technologies/ Any other domain related <br>to energy</td><td>Minimum one year&#8217;s<br>experience in the Renewable <br>Energy sector</td></tr><tr><td class="has-text-align-center" data-align="center">3</td><td>MBA (Finance)/ Chartered Accountant (CA)</td><td>Minimum one year&#8217;s<br>experience in Finance sector</td></tr><tr><td class="has-text-align-center" data-align="center">1</td><td>Graduate in law</td><td>Minimum one year&#8217;s<br>experience in the Energy<br>sector</td></tr><tr><td class="has-text-align-center" data-align="center">1</td><td>BA (Hons.) in Political Science</td><td>Handled Parliamentary<br>matters, Matters ol<br>Parliamentary Standing<br>Committees, Preparation of<br>Parliamentary Committee report,<br>Budget Matters etc.</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-aff0c80e0074f22d66d75083f6884317"><strong>Age Limit for MNRE Young Professional:</strong></p>



<p class="">Candidates should be below 30 years of age as on 13 November 2024.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-2ebda37545782c0d86674cb05e3493a8"><strong>Remuneration of MNRE Young Professional:</strong></p>



<p class="">The remuneration to these Professionals is proposed to be consolidated fee of Rs.70,000/- per month for first year, Rs.75,000/- per month for second year, and Rs.80,000/- per month for third year, for candidates who opt for three-year engagement.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-892eecb06578d8f94904cc83b5576128"><strong>Period of engagement of MNRE Young Professional:</strong></p>



<p class="">The period of engagement is proposed to be initially for one year and maximum of three years, based on year-on-year performance.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-6f13ae0996cf2ef3789d6eb5be3b269d"><strong>Job description:</strong></p>



<p class="">Young Professions will be required to provide quality inputs for the following:-<br>I. Policy research and analysis<br>II. Planning, development, management, monitoring and impact assessment of schemes and programmes.<br>Ill. Data collection and analysis<br>IV. Aiding new initiatives like hydrogen economy<br>V. Public outreach &amp; communication, activities pertaining to international relation etc.<br>Any other specific task to be assigned</p>



<p class="has-vivid-red-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-9ec0027153fd73bece10939194a1ae27"><strong>Download MNRE Young Professional Recruitment Notification:</strong> <strong><a href="https://cdnbbsr.s3waas.gov.in/s3716e1b8c6cd17b771da77391355749f3/uploads/2024/11/20241113713371736.pdf">Click Here</a></strong></p>



<p class="has-vivid-red-color has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-578b5f331ea82f35961470f61415da6b"><strong>How to Apply for MNRE Young Professional:</strong></p>



<p class="">Eligible candidates may send their application to the undersigned by e-mail at <span 
                data-original-string='cVZtsCKQQH9dkSP0e1fhHQ==242zak8IB0JJ6M1vxfeKocH1m2xBQZFNtASCy+t1poORnQ='
